title: Bonanza 44 The Savage (1960) Full Length Western

sources.title: Bonanza 44 The Savage (1960) Full Length Western
sources.description:
Adam falls for a girl (Anna-Lisa) believed by Indians to be the white buffalo woman. The tribe wants to harm her and is looking for her.
 
Director: James Neilson
Writers: Joseph Stone, Paul King
Stars: Lorne Greene, Pernell Roberts, Dan Blocker
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western
